About the game:

On a visit to her hometown, Flo and her Grandma Florence take a stroll down memory lane. Bring five restaurants back to life and meet new customers like the Hungry Man and the Celebrity in Diner Dash: Hometown Hero! Take special care of customers with reservations and keep them happy by placing flowers on tables in timely order. Are you stuck with a 4-person group and no 4-top tables? Now you can create a larger table by moving tables together in this delectable new Diner Dash game: Hometown Hero!
